para.text:
        The FileDialog widget provides a nicer, more functional
        and very powerful widget to browse for files.
          // ...
$dlg= &new FileDialog();
if (MB_OK == $dlg->show()) {           // OK pressed
  printf("File selected: %s%s\n", $dlg->getDirectory(), $dlg->getFileName());
}
// ... 
        Check out these to screenshots to see what this dialog
        window looks like:

        The MessageBox class provides an easy-to-use interface for showing messages.

          // ...
MessageBox::display(
  'Cannot load the same test config twice!', 
  'Error', 
  MB_OK | MB_ICONWARNING
);
// ... 
